''WhiteMagic''是一種由[[Sony|Sony]]開發並首用於[[Sony_Xperia_P|Sony Xperia P]]的顯示技術。這技術在平常的[[RGB|RGB]]像素中額外多加一個白色的[[子像素|子像素]]，使其每個像素都包含RGBW子像素。Sony聲稱由於白色子像素有較高[[透光度|透光度]]，所以只需要少點電作背光用即可提供同樣的亮度，達至節省電力之效。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitimes.com.tw/tw/dt/n/shwnws.asp?id=0000278195_W6K0BZ2SL9PN0S4LQYN35 |title=WhiteMagic顯示技術 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archive-date=2016-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428000849/http://www.digitimes.com.tw/tw/dt/n/shwnws.asp?id=0000278195_W6K0BZ2SL9PN0S4LQYN35 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此技術亦有由[[Japan_Display|Japan Display]]等其他公司展示。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.geek.com/mobile/japan-display-demos-whitemagic-and-pixel-eyes-display-tech-1526099/ |title=Japan Display demos WhiteMagic and Pixel Eyes display tech |access-date=2013-08-23 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924043318/http://www.geek.com/mobile/japan-display-demos-whitemagic-and-pixel-eyes-display-tech-1526099/ }}</ref>雖然此技術和[[PenTile|Pentile RGBW]]一樣有RGBW子像素，但不同於PenTile RGBW中每組RGBW子像素分屬兩個像素，每組RGBW子像素在WhiteMagic中均屬於同一個像素。這樣除了能避免了某些因PenTile而起的問題，還能在相同[[ppi|ppi]]下提供雙倍[[子像素密度|子像素密度]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/5583/sony-announces-xperia-p-and-u-joining-xperia-s |title=Sony Announces Xperia P and U, joining Xperia S NXT Series |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022053231/http://www.anandtech.com/show/5583/sony-announces-xperia-p-and-u-joining-xperia-s |dead-url=no }}</ref>

